Package: pibble
Type: Package
Title: Empirical Probability and Information Theory Operations on Categorical Tibbles
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Robert Ness
Maintainer: Robert Ness <robertness@gmail.com>
Description: Pibble provides operations useful in calculating empirical probabilities and
    information theoretic statistics on tibbles containing categorical data. It is relies on and
    plays nice with the tidyverse.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: dplyr, purrr, tidyr
LazyData: true
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
